com.yworks.yfiles.view.input

Class ReshapeRectangleContext

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.yworks.yfiles.view.input.ReshapeRectangleContext

  • public final class ReshapeRectangleContext
extends Object
    Helper class that carries information about a reshape operation.

    This class is mainly intended for use by INodeReshapeSnapResultProvider.collectSnapResults(GraphSnapContext, CollectSnapResultsEventArgs, com.yworks.yfiles.graph.INode, ReshapeRectangleContext).
